cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.CY, cs.LG 

This paper is primarily focused on the usability and security of cryptographic APIs, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the creation of an open-source web platform, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Additionally, the platform deals with cryptography (cs.CY) and potentially machine learning (cs.LG) in the future, as the platform grows and expands its capabilities.
